OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781269896
OL,3,CAsylum seeker guilty of park rape
OL,4,Cjailed and expects deportation
OL,6,FAn asylum seeker who twice raped a
OL,7,F"drunk and obviously vulnerable" woman
OL,8,Fin a park has been given a 14-year
OL,9,Fextended sentence after a court was
OL,10,Ftold he had shown no remorse.
OL,12,FPakistan-born Sheraz Malik was found
OL,13,Fguilty of two counts of rape in
OL,14,FJanuary after jurors heard how he
OL,15,Fattacked the 18-year-old woman shortly
OL,16,Fafter she had been raped by another
OL,17,Fman in Sutton Lawn park in Sutton-in-
OL,18,FAshfield in Nottinghamshire last June.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@`O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781269896
OL,3,CAsylum seeker guilty of park rape
OL,4,Cjailed and expects deportation
OL,6,FMalik, 28, formerly of Bath Street in
OL,7,FSutton-in-Ashfield, claimed he had
OL,8,Fconsensual sex with the woman, but was
OL,9,Ffound guilty after three hours of
OL,10,Fdeliberations at Birmingham Crown
OL,11,FCourt.
OL,13,FPassing sentence at the same court on
OL,14,FThursday, Judge Simon Ash KC imposed a
OL,15,F10-year jail sentence extended by an
OL,16,Fadditional four-year period on licence.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781269896
OL,3,CAsylum seeker guilty of park rape
OL,4,Cjailed and expects deportation
OL,6,FAfter being told that Malik was
OL,7,Fexpected to be deported on his
OL,8,Feventual release, the judge told him:
OL,9,F"There is no evidence of remorse or of
OL,10,Fyou having any insight into the
OL,11,Fserious harm you have caused to the
OL,12,Fvictim.
OL,14,F"You appear to feel only hostility and
OL,15,Fanger towards her."
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781269896
OL,3,CAsylum seeker guilty of park rape
OL,4,Cjailed and expects deportation
OL,6,FThe court was told Malik, who appeared
OL,7,Fin the dock dressed in a black Nike
OL,8,Ftracksuit and was assisted by a Pashto
OL,9,Finterpreter, still denies any
OL,10,Fwrongdoing and was "shouting and
OL,11,Fswearing" when a probation officer
OL,12,Fspoke to him to prepare a report in
OL,13,FFebruary.
OL,15,FThe rapist, who had been smoking
OL,16,Fcannabis and struck the victim,
OL,17,Fcutting her lip, was said by the judge
OL,18,Fto have made humiliating and degrading
OL,19,Fcomments.
OL,26,@rD@TOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781269896
OL,3,CAsylum seeker guilty of park rape
OL,4,Cjailed and expects deportation
OL,6,FThe judge told Malik: "You used
OL,7,Fviolence against her in the course of
OL,8,Fraping her.
OL,10,F"When she tried to resist you, you hit
OL,11,Fher to the face and head.
OL,13,F"The probation officer states that
OL,14,Fwhen he discussed the offending you
OL,15,Fcontinued to deny it and spoke about
OL,16,Fthe victim in a derogatory and abusive
OL,17,Fmanner."
OL,26,@nD@WOUrD@AOUuD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781269896
OL,3,CAsylum seeker guilty of park rape
OL,4,Cjailed and expects deportation
OL,6,FThe court heard the pre-sentence
OL,7,Freport noted that Malik had "distorted
OL,8,Fthinking" in relation to consent,
OL,9,Fpersonal entitlement and the
OL,10,Fobjectification of women.
OL,12,FSummarising the report, Nicholas
OL,13,FCorsellis KC, prosecuting, said Malik
OL,14,Fhad still harboured a "strong sense of
OL,15,Fgrievance and resentment" towards the
OL,16,Fwoman.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@IO]vD@WOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781269896
OL,3,CAsylum seeker guilty of park rape
OL,4,Cjailed and expects deportation
OL,6,FIn a personal impact statement prior
OL,7,Fto sentencing, the victim, who cannot
OL,8,Fbe identified, said she suffered
OL,9,Fflashbacks of the offence and had
OL,10,Ffound giving evidence at court very
OL,11,Fdifficult and very stressful.
OL,13,FPart of the statement said: "I find
OL,14,Fmyself struggling to cope.
OL,16,F"I keep having nightmares about the
OL,17,Fincident and the medical examination
OL,18,Fafter it."
OL,26,@uD@]OUxD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781269896
OL,3,CAsylum seeker guilty of park rape
OL,4,Cjailed and expects deportation
OL,6,FMalik, who lived in Italy, Germany and
OL,7,FFrance before coming to the UK, is
OL,8,Fstill awaiting the outcome of an
OL,9,Fasylum application, having been in
OL,10,FBritain for less than 12 months when
OL,11,Fhe attacked the teenager, the court
OL,12,Fwas told.
OL,14,FNottinghamshire Police is still
OL,15,Fconducting inquiries to locate and
OL,16,Farrest a further suspect alleged to
OL,17,Fhave attacked the victim.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781269896
OL,3,CAsylum seeker guilty of park rape
OL,4,Cjailed and expects deportation
OL,6,FCommenting after the sentencing,
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Nicole Milner
OL,8,Fsaid: "Above all, my thoughts are with
OL,9,Fthe victim, whose courage, resilience
OL,10,Fand bravery have been evident
OL,11,Fthroughout both the investigation and
OL,12,Fthe criminal justice process.
OL,14,F"Sheraz Malik has today received a
OL,15,Fsignificant custodial sentence,
OL,16,Freflecting the seriousness of his
OL,17,Foffending and the profound impact of
OL,18,Fhis actions on the victim.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781269896
OL,3,CAsylum seeker guilty of park rape
OL,4,Cjailed and expects deportation
OL,6,F"I hope this sentence brings the
OL,7,Fvictim a sense of justice and
OL,8,Freassurance that Malik no longer poses
OL,9,Fa threat to our community."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@[O]
